2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20surge%20of%20hateful%20incidents%20has%20coincided%20with%20rising%20tensions%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%2C%20worsening%20the%20climate%20of%20discrimination.%20However%2C%20this%20year%2C%20the%20cases%20of%20xenophobia%20can%20largely%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20anti-immigration%20rhetoric%20spread%20online%2C%20particularly%20in%20social%20media%20comment%20sections%20and%20TikTok%20clips%20mocking%20Indians.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20hate%20towards%20Indians%20and%20South%20Asians%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20normalised%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EImmigration%20Is%20Irking%20Canadians%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncreased%20immigration%20has%20reinforced%20the%20narrative%20that%20all%20current%20societal%20problems%20are%20due%20to%20immigrants.%20Sadly%2C%20the%20anti-India%20rhetoric%20is%20influencing%20public%20discourse%20and%20shaping%20harmful%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20attack%20on%20Hindu%20devotees%20at%20the%20Hindu%20Sabha%20temple%20in%20Brampton%20by%20a%20pro-Khalistani%20mob%20has%20shaken%20the%20Indian%20community.%20Once%20considered%20largely%20law-abiding%2C%20thousands%20of%20Indian-origin%20people%E2%80%94both%20Hindus%20and%20Sikhs%E2%80%94protested%20against%20the%20violence.%20It%20was%20also%20a%20demonstration%20of%20their%20unity%2C%20given%20that%20a%20small%20group%20of%20pro-Khalistanis%20have%20been%20patronised%20by%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20government%20for%20vote-bank%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20used%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20most%20accepting%20country%20in%20the%20world%20for%20migrants.%20However%2C%20things%20have%20changed%20dramatically%20on%20the%20ground.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20large%20number%20of%20Indian%20immigrants%20arriving%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20increased%20their%20presence%20in%20schools%2C%20workplaces%2C%20and%20neighbourhoods.%20This%20change%20has%20made%20some%20Canadians%20uneasy%2C%20as%20they%20see%20Indians%20as%20competition%20for%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chawla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20derogatory%20social%20media%20posts%20spreading%20falsehoods%20about%20Indians%20have%20gained%20traction%20in%20online%20publications%20and%20mainstream%20media%2C%20giving%20them%20credibility.%20In%20July%2C%20two%20posts%20about%20Indians'%20'toilet%20habits'%20went%20viral.%20One%20video%20on%20TikTok%20claimed%20that%20Indian%20immigrants%20were%20soiling%20Wasaga%20Beach%20in%20Ontario%3B%20another%20post%20on%20X%20featured%20a%20photo%20of%20a%20turbaned%20man%20allegedly%20relieving%20himself%20in%20a%20parking%20lot%20in%20Brampton.%20Later%2C%20cyber%20experts%20suggested%20that%20both%20posts%20were%20likely%20doctored%2C%20but%20this%20did%20not%20stop%20the%20chain%20of%20hate-mongering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20diplomatic%20tensions%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%2C%20Ashwin%20Annamalai%2C%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20of%20Indian%20origin%2C%20shared%20a%20disturbing%20video%20online.%20Annamalai%20was%20seen%20being%20the%20target%20of%20a%20racist%20outburst%20from%20a%20Canadian%20white%20woman%20who%20wrongly%20assumed%20he%20was%20an%20Indian%20national.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Canada's%202021%20census%2C%20Sikhs%20constituted%202.1%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20yet%20they%20remain%20frequent%20targets%20of%20racist%20stereotypes%20and%20attacks.%20As%20per%20the%20Canadian%20Race%20Relations%20Foundation%2C%20hate%20crimes%20against%20South%20Asians%20increased%20by%20143%25%20between%202019%20and%202022%2C%20and%20a%20quarter%20of%20South%20Asian-Canadians%20reported%20experiencing%20discrimination%20or%20harassment%20in%202022%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPreconceived%20notions%20about%20Indians%20being%20%E2%80%98too%20successful'%20or%20%E2%80%98too%20different'%20are%20examples%20of%20stereotypes%20that%20fuel%20prejudice.%20Xenophobic%20feelings%20were%20heightened%20by%20the%20COVID-19%20outbreak%2C%20as%20many%20people%20linked%20the%20virus%20to%20Asians%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Talwar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ENo%20Longer%20A%20'Model%20Minority'%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20been%20plagued%20with%20economic%20challenges%2C%20ranging%20from%20a%20strained%20healthcare%20system%20to%20a%20housing%20crisis%20and%20a%20rising%20cost%20of%20living.%20White%20native%20Canadians%20increasingly%20view%20immigrants%2C%20particularly%20those%20of%20Indian%20and%20South%20Asian%20origin%2C%20as%20being%20responsible%20for%20the%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20growing%20sentiment%20in%20Canada%20that%20the%20country%20has%20lost%20control%20over%20immigration.%20Immigrants%20are%20being%20blamed%20for%20the%20housing%20and%20infrastructure%20crisis%20and%20are%20seen%20as%20competing%20with%20Canadians%20for%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20September%202024%20Environics%20Focus%20Canada%20survey%20reveals%20that%2058%25%20of%20Canadians%2C%20the%20highest%20since%201998%2C%20believe%20there%20is%20too%20much%20immigration.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20recently%20made%20significant%20cuts%20to%20the%20number%20of%20immigrants%20allowed%20into%20Canada.%20The%20number%20of%20new%20permanent%20residents%20(PRs)%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20reduced%20by%20nearly%2020%25%20from%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20native%20Canadians%20no%20longer%20see%20Indians%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98model%20minority'%20since%20many%20Indian%20immigrants%20have%20succeeded%20in%20industries%20like%20technology%20and%20healthcare%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Eshan%20Sodhi%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Mississauga.%20International%20students%E2%80%94most%20of%20whom%20are%20from%20India%E2%80%94have%20also%20been%20blamed%20for%20Canada's%20housing%20woes%20and%20skyrocketing%20rents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%208%2C%20Canada%20discontinued%20the%20Student%20Direct%20Stream%20visa%20programme%20for%20international%20students.%20The%20programme%2C%20which%20specifically%20focused%20on%20bringing%20student%20immigrants%20from%2014%20countries%2C%20including%20India%2C%20was%20implemented%20by%20Immigration%2C%20Refugees%20and%20Citizenship%20Canada%20(IRCC)%20in%202018%20to%20expedite%20study%20permit%20applications.%20Sources%20suggest%20that%20the%20government%20closed%20the%20programme%20due%20to%20negative%20reactions%20from%20native%20Canadians%20over%20the%20housing%20and%20resource%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20already%20tense%20relations%20between%20Canada%20and%20India%20following%20the%20assassination%20of%20a%20prominent%20Khalistan%20separatist%20last%20year%20have%20made%20the%20situation%20even%20more%20fraught.%20The%20latest%20attack%20on%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Brampton%20has%20only%20added%20to%20the%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Khalistani%20movement%20and%20other%20political%20issues%20have%20also%20fuelled%20unfavourable%20opinions%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Canada-India%20relations.%20Finally%2C%20the%20rise%20in%20nationalism%20and%20anti-immigration%20sentiment%20has%20increased%20distrust%20toward%20immigrant%20communities%2C%20particularly%20Indians%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sodhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731496440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flqmpjav_canada_625x300_13_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-racism-against-indians-is-growing-in-canada-7009914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20has%20been%20a%20growing%20sentiment%20in%20Canada%20that%20the%20country%20has%20lost%20control%20over%20immigration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22