okehold.%20Following%20the%20strangulation%2C%20he%20reportedly%20used%20diaper%20tape%20to%20restrain%20her%20hands.%C2%A0Afterwards%2C%20he%20allegedly%20disposed%20of%C2%A0Ms%20Barbosa's%20body%20by%20throwing%20it%20over%20the%20wall%20and%20hiding%20it%20in%20an%20unoccupied%20adjacent%20property%2C%20where%20it%20was%20later%20discovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20Ms%20Barbosa's%C2%A0disappearance%20after%20her%20husband%2C%20whom%20she%20had%20married%20just%20eight%20days%20prior%2C%20reported%20her%20missing.%C2%A0The%20man%20stated%20that%20he%20took%20his%20wife%20to%20work%2C%20but%20that%20she%20had%20not%20returned%20home%20and%20was%20not%20answering%20her%20cell%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20chief%20Carlos%20Alfama%20explained%2C%20''He%20thought%20the%20victim%20had%20died%20and%20went%20to%20another%20room.%20Suddenly%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20she%20had%20regained%20consciousness%20and%20was%20trying%20to%20run%20away.%20The%20suspect%20then%20grabbed%20Cintia%20and%20allegedly%20strangled%20her%20again%20with%20masking%20tape.%C2%A0He%20strangled%20the%20victim%20with%20this%20masking%20tape%20to%20ensure%20she%20would%20die.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20investigation%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20there%20was%20disturbed%20earth%20in%20the%20backyard%20of%20the%20residence%20where%20the%20woman%20worked%20and%20that%20the%20house's%20electric%20fence%20had%20been%20pulled.%C2%A0Initially%2C%20investigators%20suspected%20that%20Santos%20may%20have%20had%20an%20accomplice%20to%20dispose%20of%20Cintia%20Ribeiro%20Barbosa's%20body%20over%20the%20wall%20into%20the%20neighbouring%20property.%20However%2C%20a%20review%20of%20security%20camera%20footage%20revealed%20no%20evidence%20of%20anyone%20else%20entering%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Alfama%20said%20that%20the%20only%20others%20present%20were%20the%20bedridden%20elderly%20couple%2C%20who%20required%20assistance%20to%20move%2C%20making%20it%20impossible%20for%20them%20to%20be%20involved.%20''He%20confessed%20to%20the%20crime%20in%20detail%20and%20confirmed%20what%20the%20security%20cameras%20also%20showed%20us.%20He%20acted%20alone%2C''%20Mr%C2%A0Alfama%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20of%20the%20caregiver%2C%20who%20preferred%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20said%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20very%20dear%20to%20the%20elderly%20couple%2C%20with%20whom%20she%20had%20worked%20for%20about%206%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731493620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F7k8gi30o_cintia-ribeiro-barbosa_625x300_13_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnewlywed-in-brazil-strangled-after-she-slapped-co-worker-who-asked-for-a-kiss-7009502%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20investigations%20revealed%20that%20Bastos%20Santos%20confessed%20to%20the%20heinous%20crime%2C%20stating%20that%20he%20strangled%20Ms%20Barbosa%20after%20she%20rejected%20his%20romantic%20advances.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhy%20India%2C%20Pak%20Not%20Getting%20Banned%3F%26quot%3B%20ICC%20Gets%20Stern%20Message%20Amid%20CT%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20wicket-keeper%20batter%20Rashid%20Malik%20says%20if%20had%20the%20power%20he%20would%20not%20let%20Pakistan%20play%20against%20India%20in%20any%20tournament%20and%20also%20suggested%20that%20ICC%20should%20not%20grant%20the%20hosting%20rights%20of%20global%20events%20to%20both%20countries%20until%20they%20resolve%20their%20issues.%20The%20BCCI%20has%20refused%20to%20send%20its%20team%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Champions%20Trophy%20and%20there%20speculation%20that%20the%20entire%20tournament%20could%20be%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20has%20written%20to%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20asking%20for%20a%20written%20confirmation%20from%20the%20BCCI%20for%20India's%20inability%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20big%20possibility%20that%20Pakistan%20can%20stop%20playing%20cricket%20against%20India.%20Had%20I%20been%20in%20power%2C%20then%2C%20yes%2C%20I%20may%20have%20taken%20this%20strong%20step.%20I%20would%20not%20blame%20anyone%20for%20this.%20If%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20play%20(in%20Pakistan)%2C%20then%20don't%20play%20against%20us%20(at%20all)%2C%26quot%3B%20Latif%2C%20known%20for%20his%20plain%20speak%2C%20told%20PTI%20Videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20would%20have%20been%20there%2C%20I%20would%20have%20taken%20this%20decision%2C%20and%20fought%20against%20the%20BCCI.%26quot%3B%20He%20suggested%20that%20the%20ICC%20should%20also%20stop%20giving%20major%20tournaments%20to%20both%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20till%20issues%20are%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20ICC%20should%20withhold%20the%20hosting%20rights%20for%20both%20countries%20until%20these%20issues%20between%20them%20are%20resolved%3B%20until%20their%20problems%20are%20settled%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20wicketkeeper-batter%20who%20played%2037%20Tests%20and%20166%20ODIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETouching%20upon%20the%20issue%20of%20political%20interference%20in%20cricket%2C%20particularly%20in%20Asia%2C%20Latif%20referred%20to%20the%20ban%20imposed%20on%20Sri%20Lanka%20(in%202023)%20and%20Zimbabwe%20(in%202019)%20by%20the%20ICC%20and%20questioned%20why%20the%20global%20body%20was%20lenient%20towards%20India%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20had%20suspended%20Sri%20Lanka%20Cricket%20(SLC)%20in%20November%20last%20year%20for%20alleged%20political%20interference%20in%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20sport%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20suspension%20was%20lifted%20in%20January%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20a