n%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Precedence%20Research%2C%20the%20global%20protein%20market%20was%20worth%20%2410.37%20billion%20in%202022%20and%20is%20forecast%20to%20grow%20to%20%2423.34%20billion%20by%202032.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20studies%20pointing%20to%20the%20potential%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultra-processed-foods-health-problems-study-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20health%20risks%20of%20UPFs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20started%20to%20wonder%20if%20I%20could%20hit%20my%20protein%20target%20while%20avoiding%20them%20and%20keeping%20my%20calories%20in%20check%20(not%20just%20stuffing%20my%20face%20with%20vast%20quantities%20of%20peanut%20butter).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20UK-based%20nutritionist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftasty-no-protein-powder-shake-reduce-ultra-processed-foods-diet-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERob%20Hobson%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20used%20to%20eat%20protein%20bars%20every%20day%20but%20cut%20down%20once%20he%20learned%20about%20the%20link%20between%20UPFs%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprocessed-food-makes-us-fat-leads-to-cancer-alternatives-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehost%20of%20health%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E%20plus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-processed-foods-lead-to-weight-gain-nih-study-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweight%20gain%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20cutting%20out%20high-protein%20UPFs%20for%20a%20week.%20There's%20no%20set%20definition%20for%20a%20UPF%2C%20but%20it's%20widely%20considered%20to%20mean%20any%20food%20or%20drink%20containing%20an%20ingredient%20you%20wouldn't%20have%20in%20your%20own%20kitchen%2C%20such%20as%20emulsifiers.%20So%20that's%20how%20I%20chose%20what%20to%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20doable%20but%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%2C%20and%20my%20diet%20also%20became%20more%20boring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20four%20lessons%20I%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238913cfb-71b0-431d-91b2-366274f87893%5C%22%3EI%20had%20to%20pay%20close%20attention%20to%20ingredient%20lists%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20before%20I%20started%20my%20experiment%2C%20I%20made%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthy-oat-based-breakfast-recipes-for-fat-loss-muscle-gain-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eovernight%20oats%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20following%20morning%20%E2%80%94%20without%20my%20usual%20scoop%20of%20protein%20powder.%20Instead%2C%20Greek%20yogurt%20and%20chia%20provided%20protein%2C%20and%20honey%20gave%20flavor%20and%20sweetness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20I%20was%20lying%20in%20bed%20that%20night%20that%20I%20realized%20I'd%20unthinkingly%20used%20almond%20milk%20%E2%80%94%20a%20UPF%20%E2%80%94%20as%20I%20would%20normally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20a%20great%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20overnight%20oats%2C%20and%20a%20grilled%20cheese%20with%20soup.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67334368192f52589857cd06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOvernight%20oats%2C%20and%20a%20grilled%20cheese%20sandwich%20with%20soup.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECome%20lunchtime%2C%20and%20having%20not%20had%20time%20to%20go%20to%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20I%20assessed%20the%20bread%20options%20in%20the%20freezer.%20One%20loaf%20was%20UPF%2C%20one%2C%20fortunately%2C%20wasn't.%20While%20I%20was%20already%20aware%20of%20%26quot%3Bsourfaux%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20fake%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fis-sourdough-bread-healthy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esourdough%20bread%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20I%20decided%20to%20pay%20more%20attention%20to%20which%20bread%20I%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20pleased%20to%20find%20that%20the%20store-bought%20soup%20in%20my%20fridge%20was%20not%20a%20UPF%20either.%20So%20my%20go-to%20winter%20lunch%20of%20soup%20with%20a%20grilled%20cheese%20sandwich%20on%20sourdough%20bread%20was%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20went%20to%20the%20store%2C%20however%2C%20I%20realized%20not%20all%20soups%20are%20created%20equal%2C%20and%20sadly%20some%20of%20my%20favorites%20were%20UPFs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2264dcae4a-bfba-43ed-b594-1d4e97c323c3%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20like%20feeling%20that%20foods%20were%20off-limits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20to%20think%20of%20high-protein%20snacks%20to%20eat%20aside%20from%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fis-greek-yogurt-good-for-you%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreek%20yogurt%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20days%20I%20had%20an%20apple%20with%20peanut%20butter%2C%20but%20that%20got%20boring%20after%20a%20while%20and%20isn't%20as%20high%20in%20protein%20as%20some%20people%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESatisfying%20my%20sweet%20tooth%20wasn't%20particularly%20easy%20either%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20always%20want%20high-protein%20snacks%2C%20sometimes%20I%20just%20want%20a%20sweet%20treat.%20Nothing%20in%20my%20food%20cupboard%20was%20UPF-free%2C%20and%20I%20realized%20I'd%20have%20to%20bake%20from%20scratch%2C%20so%20blueberry%20muffins%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20gazed%20longingly%20at%20the%20chocolate%20in%20my%20cupboard%2C%20I%20started%20to%20feel%20uneasy.%20Having%20food%20%26quot%3Boff-limits%26quot%3B%20felt%20all%20too%20familiar.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20being%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-calorie-counting-helped-me-improve-my-relationship-with-food-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethroes%20of%20diet%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%2010%20or%20so%20years%20ago%2C%20back%20when%20I%20thought%20certain%20foods%20were%20%26quot%3Bbad%26quot%3B%20(which%2C%20of%20course%2C%20made%20me%20want%20them%20even%20more).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who's%20come%20a%20long%20way%20and%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20into%20breaking%20free%20from%20this%20restrictive%20mindset%2C%20I%20didn't%20like%20the%20feeling%20that%20there%20were%20foods%20I%20couldn't%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226525d738-ab03-4a84-85a2-8261bdd9fa10%5C%22%3ESmall%20swaps%20helped%20me%20avoid%20UPFs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20cook%20dinners%20from%20scratch%20and%20I%20realized%20I%20could%20make%20small%20tweaks%20to%20ensure%20they%20were%20UPF-free.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20like%20making%20pasta%20sauces%20with%20cream%20cheese%2C%20but%20I%20realized%20that%20some%20brands%20were%20UPF%20and%20others%20weren't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrocery%20shopping%20took%20longer%20than%20usual%2C%20but%20I%20figured%20that%20was%20inevitable%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20experiment%20and%20it%20would%20become%20less%20time-consuming%20as%20I%20learned%20which%20foods%20were%20UPF-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20pea%20pasta%20with%20chicken%2C%20chickpeas%2C%20butternut%20squash%2C%20leeks%2C%20and%20pine%20nuts%3B%20and%20a%20blueberry%20muffin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673343aa5ec9bfa3d63d73b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPea%20pasta%20with%20chicken%2C%20chickpeas%2C%20butternut%20squash%2C%20leeks%2C%20and%20pine%20nuts%3B%20and%20a%20blueberry%20muffin.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20meat-eater%2C%20I%20find%20it%20easy%20to%20eat%20enough%20protein%20at%20dinner%2C%20and%20I%20regularly%20make%20dishes%20combining%20both%20meat%20and%20pulses%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20chili%20con%20carne%20with%20black%20beans%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20varied%20nutrients%20they%20provide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20was%20conscious%20of%20needing%20my%20dinner%20to%20do%20even%20more%20heavy%20lifting%20to%20hit%20my%20protein%20goal%20while%20avoiding%20UPFs.%20So%20I%20opted%20for%20pea%20pasta%20rather%20than%20the%20usual%20wholewheat%2C%20which%20contained%2015%20grams%20more%20protein%20per%20100%20grams.%20I%20preferred%20the%20texture%20and%20taste%20of%20regular%20pasta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c717432d-4e4c-4f3c-a273-70b90a629772%5C%22%3EMy%20diet%20was%20more%20boring%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20week%20wore%20on%2C%20I%20got%20bored%20of%20eating%20the%20same%20meals.%20The%20cinnamon%20and%20raisin%20bagels%20in%20the%20freezer%20and%20the%20cereal%20in%20my%20cupboard%20teased%20me%20as%20I%20ate%20the%20same%20two%20breakfasts%20on%20repeat%20(overnight%20oats%20with%20cow's%20milk%20and%20sourdough%20toast%20with%20a%20side%20of%20Greek%20yogurt).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sure%20I%20could%20have%20been%20more%20experimental%2C%20but%20avoiding%20UPFs%20was%20taking%20enough%20planning%20without%20having%20to%20find%20new%20recipes%20to%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20managed%20to%20hit%20my%20protein%20target%20of%20110%20to%20130%20grams%20of%20protein%20each%20day%2C%20but%20my%20diet%20felt%20a%20bit%20less%20exciting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECome%20the%20weekend%2C%20when%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20wanted%20to%20order%20a%20pizza%2C%20I%20decided%20that%20life%20was%20too%20short%20to%20miss%20out%2C%20even%20for%20a%20one-off%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20while%20most%20dietitians%20advise%20people%20to%20take%20a%20food-first%20approach%20to%20hitting%20their%20various%20health%20targets%2C%20they%20aren't%20saying%20people%20need%20to%20eliminate%20UPFs%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-people-make-cutting-down-ultra-processed-foods-dietitian-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D