ik%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalik%20also%20faced%20a%20similar%20controversy%20after%20a%20video%20showing%20her%20in%20an%20intimate%20moment%20with%20her%20partner%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20in%20October.%20She%20claimed%20the%20video%20was%20%26quot%3Bfake%26quot%3B%20and%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20Federal%20Investigation%20Agency%20(FIA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Malik%20faced%20intense%20trolling%20since%20social%20media%20users%20accused%20her%20of%20intentionally%20leaking%20the%20video.%20Pakistani%20actress%20Mishi%20Khan%20released%20a%20video%20in%20which%20she%20criticised%20influencers%20%26quot%3Bstooping%20to%20the%20lowest%20level%26quot%3B%20for%20fame.%20She%20did%20not%20directly%20name%20Malik%2C%20but%20the%20references%20were%20said%20to%20be%20directed%20towards%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731489900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fijuvlnso_imsha-rehman_625x300_13_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistani-influencer-imsha-rehman-deactivates-social-media-accounts-after-private-video-leaks-7008463%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Before%20deactivating%20her%20account%2C%20Imsha%20Rehman%20talked%20about%20dealing%20with%20negative%20comments%2C%20according%20to%20local%20media.%20She%20called%20the%20backlash%20%26quot%3Boverwhelming%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Rajasthan%20Official%20Slapped%20By%20Independent%20Candidate%20Outside%20Booth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shocking%20incident%20at%20a%20Rajasthan%20polling%20booth%2C%20Naresh%20Meena%2C%20an%20independent%20candidate%20from%20the%20Deoli-Uniara%20constituency%2C%20was%20captured%20on%20video%20slapping%20a%20Sub-Divisional%20Magistrate%20(SDM).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%2