20strike%20rate%20being%20below%20135%20during%20the%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20Rahul%20mentioned%20the%20need%20to%20maintain%20a%20balanced%20culture%20and%20team%20atmosphere%20within%20a%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20play%20in%20a%20team%20atmosphere%20where%20it%20is%20lighter.%20Dressing%20rooms%20like%20GT%20(Gujarat%20Titans)%20and%20CSK%20(Chennai%20Super%20Kings)%20seem%20balanced%20and%20calm%20even%20when%20they%20lose%2C%20and%20that%20is%20important%20to%20me%20as%20a%20player%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tried%20that%20at%20LSG%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Andy%20Flower%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F189-andy-flower-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAndy%20Flower%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20GG%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E)%20at%20first%2C%20and%20then%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Justin%20Langer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F267-justin-langer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJustin%20Langer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it%20was%20brilliant.%20But%20sometimes%20you%20have%20to%20move%20away%20and%20find%20something%20for%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20will%20go%20under%20the%20hammer%20in%20the%20IPL%202025%20mega%20auction%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20on%20November%2024%20and%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731463980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F0ivg9ee8_kl-rahul-sanjeev-goenka_625x300_28_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fsanjiv-goenkas-blunt-team-before-statement-triggered-kl-rahul-to-leave-lsg-star-breaks-silence-7004864%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20the%20retention%20announcement%2C%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20owner