0says%20Bhati.%20This%20trust%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20strong%20relationships%20they%E2%80%99ve%20built%20within%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKeeping%20the%20music%20alive%3A%20Supporting%20artists%20through%20the%20pandemic%20and%20beyond%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20folk%20artists%2C%20their%20livelihood%20depends%20entirely%20on%20their%20ability%20to%20perform%2C%20but%20during%20the%20COVID%20lockdown%2C%20when%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20the%20stage%2C%20the%20impact%20was%20devastating%20for%20entire%20communities.%20To%20support%20them%2C%20Sharon%20facilitated%20a%20collaboration%20with%20My%20Mensa%2C%20a%20visual%20learning%20app%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F300577%2Fbest-folk-artists-and-artisans-take-masterclasses-on-first-culture-tech-platform-memeraki%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20offering%20these%20artists%20opportunities%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20live%20music%20sessions.%20This%20initiative%20ensured%20that%20the%20artists%20were%20fairly%20compensated%2C%20while%20also%20driving%20increased%20app%20traffic%20and%20downloads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20had%20to%20sit%20at%20home%20and%20do%20some%20of%20the%20work%2C%20so%20we%20were%20fine%20doing%20it%20for%20free%2C%20but%20the%20artists%20needed%20to%20be%20paid%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20our%20only%20condition%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20peak%20months%20of%20COVID-19%2C%20they%20successfully%20hosted%20live%20sessions%20on%20the%20app%2C%20allowing%20every%20participating%20artist%20to%20receive%20compensation.%20This%20initiative%20also%20encouraged%20greater%20involvement%20from%20women%2C%20as%20it%20eliminated%20the%20need%20for%20them%20to%20travel%2C%20enabling%20those%20who%20had%20only%20sung%20for%20their%20families%20to%20showcase%20their%20talent%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%