on%2C%20she%20founded%20Salem%20People%20Trust%20(SPT).%20Since%202007%2C%20SPT%20has%20rescued%20and%20rehabilitated%20376%20bonded%20labourers%2C%20helped%201%2C372%20children%20return%20to%20school%20free%20from%20bonded%20labour%2C%20and%20continues%20to%20advocate%20for%20child%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20our%20initial%20focus%20was%20on%20ending%20bonded%20labour%2C%20we%20are%20proud%20to%20have%20freed%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20those%20affected%2C%20with%20their%20children%20now%20attending%20school.%20Our%20board%20members%20and%20staff%20are%20chosen%20from%20former%20bonded%20labourers%20and%20others%20with%20lived%20experiences%2C%20including%20child%20labour%20and%20the%20pressures%20of%20sex-selective%20abortion.%20We%20believe%20those%20who%20have%20lived%20through%20these%20challenges%20are%20best%20positioned%20to%20serve%20as%20community%20organisers%20and%20leaders.%20Their%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20allows%20us%20to%20effectively%20address%20the%20needs%20and%20bring%20meaningful%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20women%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20with%20flexible%20funding%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20often%20overlook%20that%20NGOs%20and%20their%20leaders%20need%20support%20to%20sustain%20their%20invaluable%20work.%20Office%20infrastructure%2C%20staff%20medical%20insurance%2C%20well-being%2C%20and%20capacity-building%20all%20demand%20investment%20beyond%20traditional%20community%20programmes%20to%20empower%20them%20to%20continue%20their%20efforts%20sustainably%20and%20without%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20flexible%20funding%20enables%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20with%20flexible%20support%20from%20the%20Rebuild%20India%20Fund%2C%20Jayam%20%3Cem%3EAkka%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20not%20only%20supporting%2010%20fellows%20to%20teach%20in%20five%20schools%20and%20organising%2020%20children%E2%80%99s%20coll