0commonplace%20in%20South%20Asian%20kitchens%20had%20become%20shadowed%20by%20contemporary%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sparked%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Cem%3EForgotten%20Foods%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20attempt%20to%20ensure%20these%20dishes%20are%20not%20obliterated%20from%20history%20altogether.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20the%20anthology%20is%20a%20coming%20together%20of%20historians%2C%20scholars%2C%20plant%20scientists%2C%20heritage%20practitioners%2C%20writers%2C%20and%20chefs%20%E2%80%94%20attempting%20to%20do%20due%20diligence%20by%20South%20Asian%20cuisine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20contributors%20is%20Sikander%20Malik.%20In%20his%20essay%2C%20Sikander%20articulates%20his%20love%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Egupchup%20shami%20kababs%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20out%20of%20minced%20%3Cem%3Eqeema%3C%2Fem%3E%20(meat)%20instead%20of%20meat%20pieces%20%E2%80%9Cor%20the%20long-cut%20%3Cem%3Eparchas%3C%2Fem%3E%20primarily%20used%20for%20%3Cem%3Epasandas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20As%20for%20what%20lent%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekababs%20%3C%2Fem%3Etheir%20tenderness%2C%20he%20writes%2C%20it%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekachumber%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20recipe%20of%20which%20he%20divulges%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fshami-kebabs-2-1730814157.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bold%20flavours%20of%20South%20Asian%20cuisine%20have%20shaped%20many%20delicacies%20of%20today.%20This%20is%20explored%20in%20Forgotten%20Foods%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fshami-kebabs-2-1730814157.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fshami-kebabs-2-1730814157-300x157.