D%20His%20fellow%20inmates%20would%20cling%20to%20these%20words%20of%20encouragement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Akshay%2C%20the%20group%20would%20head%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F303942%2Famazon-future-engineer-programme-helps-teachers-students-learn-coding-computer-science-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesignated%20computer%20centre%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20jail%20quarters%2C%20where%20Word%2C%20Excel%2C%20and%20the%20basics%20of%20typing%20would%20occupy%20them%20for%20the%20next%20few%20hours.%20These%20masterclasses%20were%20brought%20to%20them%20by%20the%20Delhi-based%20India%20Vision%20Foundation%2C%20which%2C%20for%20three%20decades%2C%20has%20aimed%20its%20programmes%20at%20rehabilitating%20and%20reintegrating%20incarcerated%20individuals%20into%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20founder%2C%20Dr%20Kiran%20Bedi%2C%20the%20first%20woman%20IPS%20(Indian%20Police%20Service)%20officer%2C%20launched%20the%20foundation%20with%20the%20prize%20money%20from%20her%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20(1994).%20Through%20a%20host%20of%20programmes%2C%20the%20non-profit%20has%20been%20championing%20reforms%20in%20the%20prison%20system%2C%20both%20among%20inmates%20and%20officers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIndia-Vision-Foundation-prison-system-reforms-1730725101.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Kiran%20Bedi%20started%20the%20India%20Vision%20Foundation%20to%20bring%20reforms%20into%20the%20prison%20system%20in%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIndia-Vision-Foundation-pri